# Docs + Speckit workflow

## Agent auto-skills

| Agent | Skills invoked automatically |
|-------|------------------------------|
| `@ba` | `speckit-specify`, `speckit-clarify`, `speckit-tasks` |
| `@be` | `speckit-plan`, `speckit-implement` |
| `@fe` | `speckit-plan`, `speckit-implement` |
| `@qa` | `speckit-checklist`, `speckit-analyze` |

## Language

Chat in any language; **docs/features/** output **English only** (`english-only-file-edits.mdc`).

## Phase order (do not skip)

1. **spec.md** — `@ba` `/speckit-specify`
2. **tasks.md** — `/speckit-tasks` (from spec)
3. **plan.md** + **be-implement.md** + **fe-implement.md** — `@be` `@fe` `/speckit-plan`
4. **implement** — `/speckit-implement` → `be/`, `fe/`
5. **test** — `@qa` `/speckit-checklist`, `make test`

## Flat feature folder

```text
spec.md → tasks.md → plan.md → be-implement.md → fe-implement.md → (code) → qa-checklist.md
```

No role subfolders.

Prompts: [`docs/workflow/agent-prompts.md`](../../docs/workflow/agent-prompts.md)
